<doc id="1239643" wikidata="Q58687" url="?curid=1239643" title="Lusciano">
<text>Lusciano is a &quot;comune&quot; in the province of Caserta in Campania, Italy. Between 1929 and 1946, it was part of the &quot;comune&quot; of Aversa.

==Neighbouring communes==
*Aversa
*Trentola-Ducenta
*Parete
*Giugliano in Campania

